premise_source_doc_sentence: He first appeared in the summer of 1942 in Wonder Woman # 1 , volume 1 , written by Wonder Woman creator William Moulton Marston , and went on to become one of Wonder Woman 's principal Golden Age foes .
The Earth-Two Wonder Woman was first featured as a character separate from Wonder Woman  (  known as Earth-One Wonder Woman  )  in the second Jay Garrick and Barry Allen comic .
The Wonder Woman Chronicles : Volume 2 collects material from Wonder Woman # 2 -- 3 , Sensation Comics # 10 -- 14 , and Comic Cavalcade # 1 ; December 6 , 2011 ; ISBN 978-1-4012-3240-5
A major adversary of Wonder Woman , the Duke is a demigod of deceit , originally presented as an operative of Wonder Woman 's nemesis Mars/Ares .
In 2016 , the Duke of Deception was re-introduced in DC Comics ' successful The Legend of Wonder Woman , an ongoing series retelling Wonder Woman 's origin .
